Item 1.02.   Termination of a Material Definitive Agreement.
 
On November 30, 2005, the Board of Directors of Benchmark Electronics, Inc. (the Company) approved the termination of the Company's Employee Stock Purchase Plan, as amended, at the end of the current offering period.  The current offering period ends December 31, 2005.  Subsequent to this date, shares will no longer be offered under the Company's Employee Stock Purchase Plan.
 
 
