Note ISubsequent Events
On October 16, 2006, the Company entered an agreement, subject to shareholder approval, with Benchmark Electronics, Inc. ("Benchmark") and Autobahn Acquisition Corp. in which shareholders of Pemstar Inc. will receive 0.160 shares of Benchmark common shares for each held Pemstar Inc. share.  Shareholder approval was received and the merger closed on January 8, 2007.  At the time of the merger closing, present Pemstar Inc. shareholders owned approximately 11% of the outstanding Benchmark common shares and Pemstar Inc. has ceased to be a separate publicly owned company.
