ions of the Company under this Agreement.  If the Company is required to provide an amount of cash collateral hereunder as a result of the occurrence of an Event of Default, such amount (to the extent not applied as aforesaid) shall be returned to the Company within three Business Days after all Events of Default have been cured or waived.  If the Company is required to provide an amount of cash collateral hereunder pursuant to , such amount (to the extent not applied as aforesaid) shall be returned
