(k)           one or more judgments for the payment of money in an aggregate amount in excess of $25,000,000 shall be rendered against the Company, any Subsidiary or any combination thereof and the same shall remain undischarged for a period of 30 consecutive days during which execution shall not be effectively stayed, or any action shall be legally taken by a
judgment creditor to attach or levy upon any assets of the Company or any Subsidiary to enforce any such judgment;
 
