. The Company will not permit (a) the EBITDA of Domestic Subsidiaries that are not Material Domestic Subsidiaries to exceed 10% of EBITDA of the Company and the Domestic Subsidiaries on a consolidated basis or (b) the combined assets of Domestic Subsidiaries that are not Material Domestic Subsidiaries to exceed 10% of the assets of the Company and the Domestic Subsidiaries taken as a whole.
